	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Small update for NINA-03/06 copynes plugin</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />By default, this plugin assumes a minimum of 16K PRG and 16K PRG. The AVE game "Pyramid" (and possibly others) has only a 8KB CHR ROM, hence it would get overdumped to 16KB. This update simply changes the minimum CHR size to 8KB.
<br />
<br />You could also get around this by simply dumping the cart as if it were an NROM cart. Even though Pyramid works fine as mapper 0, I figure it should still be set to mapper 79 since it uses that board, albeit none of it's features.
<br />
<br />You can get the updated plugin <a href="http://webpages.charter.net/bootgod/NINA0X.zip" class="postlink">here</a>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


